name: Distilabs, Inc.
description: Developer of message cleanup technologies designed to improve communication tools. The company's technology provides communication tools and email services with the use of different clean up tools as well as permits the deletion of hundreds of messages and emails at one time, enabling clients to communicate and access information in new and different ways.
